itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T22:39:09.000Z","msg":"Chopin ballade No.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定唔係最難，但好正"},{"pid":"efa413bb7b7a7273da5b4fd72350283ca270c494","tid":334282,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Chopin ballade No.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定唔係最難，但好正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚好聽"},{"pid":"6fea6a95db9a021a5d2b2115a431e745db5f62d2","tid":334282,"uid":80089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Chopin ballade No.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定唔係最難，但好正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚好聽</blockquote><br />\nScherzo no.2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a51f991227134ec67e75d776f4852864a92c03","tid":334282,"uid":126247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:58:29.000Z","msg":"hungarian rhapsody no. 2"},{"pid":"96699de1e75e02009f8cfac004aabaa098844547","tid":334282,"uid":67231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"Scarbo from Gaspard de la nuit"},{"pid":"484adb3c73688d210ace618db905c904181f4c98","tid":334282,"uid":67231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>rach 3</blockquote><br />\n都話唔計piano concerto<br />\n(其實我估到你地咁答先講明唔計）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaspard_de_la_nuit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGaspard_de_la_nuit&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=48ce1f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaspard_de_la_nuit</a><br />\n<br />\n除左堆鳩作亂黎既, Gaspard de la nuit一定算最難之一。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"3a0cc8b75decb68f256bae5fa577dd8084e5eb32","tid":334282,"uid":60131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Chopin ballade No.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定唔係最難，但好正</blockquote><br />\n至少4都難過佢，Chopin是但一首sonata都係難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw，Beethoven 106<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由頭難到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1st movement爆炸性強，本身要彈得華麗、chord等等要清晰已經唔容易，中段仲有一連串counterpoint<br />\n2nd movement相對地易，但都甚難，係structure算厚嘅scherzo，recapitulation前嘅一串F major scale亦好難彈好<br />\n3rd movement非常厚(容許我講句Brahms真係有佢影子)，全首長而深沉，彈好每一個chord而不失連貫性已經好考功夫，仲未計情感上嘅演繹<br />\n4th movement，不解釋，睇得明份譜當你贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，去音樂<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UXsgX2U_TVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUXsgX2U_TVc&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ade9d883\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UXsgX2U_TVc</a>"},{"pid":"7895c72983b157c1c0b86f382bf0b02eb28e8fa0","tid":334282,"uid":60131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>rach 3</blockquote><br />\n都話唔計piano concerto<br />\n(其實我估到你地咁答先講明唔計）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaspard_de_la_nuit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGaspard_de_la_nuit&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=48ce1f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaspard_de_la_nuit</a><br />\n<br />\n除左堆鳩作亂黎既, Gaspard de la nuit一定算最難之一。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"f65c8677132b52f2904a6cd0b502f69345d350d6","tid":334282,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"Schumann 首 toccata in C 點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24857a36fa812859a45553f53dd04e95b03c388","tid":334282,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4&lsquo;33</blockquote><br />\n比你講左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086370a59d33eb8781d7a2f0f5524e9b0910c3bb","tid":334282,"uid":60131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4&lsquo;33</blockquote><br />\n嚴格嚟講4'33&quot;冇指明係鋼琴作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0c79478a2c8978c3abb18aedb48281401fdcc0","tid":334282,"uid":60131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Schumann 首 toccata in C 點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n技巧上算難，層次上唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d79e3822f0c18996732cf06d5f2ddcb2b9a8c6","tid":334282,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Schumann 首 toccata in C 點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n技巧上算難，層次上唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點為之層次上難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c88769ea8d19eeee5b690d2bbed4c07faaa6dd","tid":334282,"ui